title: Flight Simulator 2020 - POI's - Italy - Castle Of Corigliano Calabro
description:
In this video we will fly over the Castle Of Corigliano Calabro.The fortress is reputed to be one of the most beautiful and best-preserved castles in southern Italy. Its creation is associated with the figure of the Norman king Robert Guiscardo, who commissioned the construction of a medieval fortress. Currently, the castle is a national monument and a local museum of history and art.
